article_title: Watch Interns Make A Run For It At The Supreme Court Video
article_text:
Reaction to Supreme Court Ruling on Obamacare

For the second time in three years, the Supreme Court strikes down a challenge to Obamacare. While the President and supporters are taking a victory lap, opponents like House speaker John Boehner are finding the ruling hard to swallow.
